title: MC Chris - Eatings Not Cheating/Dungeon Master (Apple Lossless)

MC Chris is mostly known for his work on [adult swim]. On Aqua Teen Hunger Force he voices "Mc Pee Pants", on Sealab 2021 he voiced "Hesh", and on Frisky Dingo he voiced "Wendell".

This 3-disc set includes direct cd rips of the albums "Eating's Not Cheating" "Eating's Not Cheating (DC Flag Edition)" & "Dungeon Master Of Ceremonies" from the Nerdcore rapper "MC Chris." These albums were ripped in Apple Lossless (.m4a) format to maintain lossless audio quality and perfection. The format is easily converted to .flac (for those of you that don't like iTunes).
